latestIgtvVideos.title: CHILD SAFETY
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
How can you fight child sexual abuse online? 
Report & don’t Share it. 
Why images and videos of child abuse circulate on social media? Because people are re-sharing out of outrage, horror and shock. 
But liking, commenting, or sharing causes more harm to the child. If you see a similar content online, please report it immediately and do not share it. Your simple act can protect a child. 

To report a content where a child is at risk, call 1098 and report to Childline India Foundation. If you see this content on Facebook, Instagram or WhatsApp, report it at fb.me/onlinechildprotection. 

Help a child. Report it. Don’t Share it.
#reportdontshare #childsafety #socialcause

latestPosts.caption:
As 2024 draws to a close, I find myself reflecting on an incredible year, one filled with moments that have truly touched my heart and soul. This year has been a journey of unforgettable experiences, from thrilling travels that expanded my horizons to quiet moments of peace and reflection. Every step along the way, I have been blessed to witness the beauty of life in ways I never imagined.

The highlight of 2024 was undoubtedly meeting the love of my life. From the moment we crossed paths, everything changed. Our connection was immediate, and in the blink of an eye, we were engaged, building a future together. This incredible bond has filled my heart with love, joy, and gratitude. I will forever cherish this special chapter of our story.

Work has been equally fulfilling. I’ve had the opportunity to grow professionally and thrive in a career I am passionate about. Every challenge has been a chance to learn, and every success, a reminder of how far I’ve come.

On a deeper level, this year has also been one of significant spiritual growth. I’ve felt a renewed connection with my faith and a profound sense of gratitude for the blessings that have come my way. The strength, wisdom, and peace I’ve received from my spiritual journey have been priceless.
Most of all, I am deeply thankful to God for every gift—big and small—that He has given me this year. The love, the opportunities, the moments of joy, and even the challenges that helped me grow have all been a part of His beautiful plan. I am forever grateful.

Thank you to everyone who has been a part of this amazing year. Your love, support, and friendship have made 2024 unforgettable. Here’s to the future, with hope and excitement for what’s to come.

#2024 #memories #goodbye2024❤️❤️
